### 1) Process Data
POST http://localhost:8080/process-data
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_id": "lingxing_7469",
  "window_days": 3,
  "target_acos": 28,
  "upper_acos": 35,
  "lower_acos": 20,
  "traffic_click_threshold": 20,
  "conversion_cvr_threshold": 0.1,
  "persist": true
}

### 2) Learn Rules
POST http://localhost:8080/learn-rules
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_id": "lingxing_7469",
  "min_samples": 4,
  "min_win_rate": 0.55,
  "min_clicks_threshold": 10,
  "cvr_weight": 0.35,
  "outlier_iqr_k": 1.5,
  "enable_outlier_filter": true,
  "include_strategy_baseline": true,
  "max_rules": 30
}

### 3) Generate Lingxing Rules
POST http://localhost:8080/generate-rules
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_id": "lingxing_7469",
  "active_only": true,
  "max_rules": 30
}

### 4) Evaluate Rules
POST http://localhost:8080/evaluate-rules
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_id": "lingxing_7469",
  "update_rules": true,
  "observations": [
    {
      "rule_id": "R001",
      "before_acos": 38.0,
      "after_acos": 31.0,
      "before_clicks": 45,
      "after_clicks": 42,
      "before_cvr": 0.09,
      "after_cvr": 0.1
    }
  ]
}

### 5) List Rules
GET http://localhost:8080/rules?store_id=lingxing_7469&active_only=true&limit=200
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
